This is a new version from JumpInCode.vim I don't know why i can't upload a new version to the old JumpInCode page (http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=2770)? So I start this branch

\"EN\"
ctags and cscope plugin, more convenice way to use ctags and cscope in vim

Command:
\sy   Generate tags and cscope database from current directory
\sc   Configure window (Take care of the help info the window below)

:VTStart  Start virtual tags (a better way to use ctgas)
:VTStop  Stop virtual tags
                  
Requirement:
Unix:   ctags and cscope
Win32: ctags.exe and cscope.exe  (win32 ctags and cscope could download from:http://code.google.com/p/easy-vim/downloads/list)

\"中文  ZH\"
自动生成并使用ctags和cscope

命令：
\sy   从当前目录生成tags和cscope.out
\sc   配置窗口 (注意配置窗口底部的帮助信息)

系统要求：
预安装要求ctags和cscope:
Unix:    ctags and cscope
Win32: ctags and cscope  （win32版的ctags和cscope下载地址：http://code.google.com/p/easy-vim/downloads/list&#65289;

